tasks.description:
Create a customer managed policy named LoanFlowSelfServiceIAM granting:
- iam:GetUser on resource arn:aws:iam::*:user/${aws:username} (own user only)
- iam:ChangePassword on resource arn:aws:iam::*:user/${aws:username}
- iam:CreateAccessKey, iam:DeleteAccessKey, iam:UpdateAccessKey, iam:ListAccessKeys on resource arn:aws:iam::*:user/${aws:username}
- iam:CreateVirtualMFADevice, iam:EnableMFADevice, iam:DeactivateMFADevice, iam:DeleteVirtualMFADevice, iam:ListMFADevices on resource * (MFA devices require * resource)
The ${aws:username} policy variable scopes all write actions to the authenticated user's own IAM user object. Attach to all six groups.
